title: 08/30/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP's joined by the MMQB's Albert Breer who discusses the possibility of a Deshaun Watson trade. Former NFL QB David Carr explains why Aaron Rodgers had full leverage during his hold out with the Packers. And Dan poses the question, what does booing your team accomplish?
